177
00:09:54,570 --> 00:09:56,200
[A glance into the center of the room
reveals a person amongst the bottles.]
[No, a broken puppet doll is lying on the floor.]
[Help it up and repair it?]
[Yes / No]

178
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,950
